{"tid":1374311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於前線同後線分歧","createTime":"2019-07-27T18:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T19:17:02.000Z","uid":292125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"673074809f39583b8bce1967af2702a5d5ce630d","tid":1374311,"uid":292125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 係P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講 今日元朗成件事雖然言論上大家仍然係三不 但睇得出大家分歧幾大<br />\n先講自己立場 我偏向幫前線 前線一直表現理智及有效 <br />\n我地後勤做好自己就好 唔洗擔心前線 只要同進同退就好<br />\n<br />\n今日睇返 &quot;無神論者的巴別塔&quot; 段片 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SHQ13r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SHQ13r&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F1z2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=ab155e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SHQ13r</a><br />\n有幾個位我覺得好中 <br />\n1. 後勤要退可以 但一定要先同前線講 <br />\n    傾掂既 前線先安排時間再度路線<br />\n    後勤比前線走先 根本等於留前線於死地 同進同退呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 溝通出現問題 <br />\n    我唔敢講有人騎劫廣播 但消息容易有錯係肯定既 尤其今次冇大台<br />\n    留意到巴絲建議用旗號去溝通 感覺可行 <br />\n    不如製作一份 之後揾前線同廣播傾下?<br />\n<br />\n而今日活動風險太高呀 老弱應唔應該黎呀 我唔特別諗 玩法好復雜<br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fa71b4379e28cd1d845e980c8cc2f109458dd7","tid":1374311,"uid":292125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"c0a0ed590c5e8ac82c8d3559ab2afaa6fcb9597d","tid":1374311,"uid":292125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:40:45.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cd679642961f72a716fa46536d4b81fd7aa8ba","tid":1374311,"uid":292125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:17:02.000Z","msg":"最後一下自push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}